&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage a team of engineers with full accountability for their performance, growth, and wellbeing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own 1:1s, performance reviews, and career development conversations — providing direct, constructive feedback that helps engineers grow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a team culture that is organized, reliable, and focused on impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor engineers through code reviews, pairing, and delivery coaching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the VP on people concerns that require escalation; help shape the team&#39;s working norms and resolve friction before it compounds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
