&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree from a four-year college or university is preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technologies: MS Office Suite of Products (Excel, Word, PowerPoint)
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior CRM experience / knowledge is preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
